      <textAnnotation id="sid-BA64E466-A6BD-46FB-901B-17A8F70DE623" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>In case of Inter Company PO (SO-PO Model), the price will be derived from receiving plant  </text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-5142449E-CE8F-4199-A6C9-1C1383926255" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Process Tower: Procure To Pay
Process Group: Procure Materials and Services (Direct &amp; Indirect)
Process: PM-080-050 Create and Process Purchase Order</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-93E131CD-5B75-4BB3-A944-03EEF8D357DB" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="" fill="#ff0000" fontFamily="" fontSize="" italic="" ref="text-left"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="" fill="#ff0000" fontFamily="" fontSize="" italic="" ref="text-right"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Flow has been migrated to BIC. Please inform the process steward Tung, Alfie Him Yeong &lt;alfie.him.yeong.tung@intel.com&gt; and BPM Champions D'Elia, Traci &lt;traci.delia@intel.com&gt;,Newman, Jennifer &lt;jennifer.newman@intel.com&gt;of any design changes that occur within the flow moving forward. This will enable us to reflect those changes in the BIC and WIKI business process documentation.</text>
      </textAnnotation>
   </process>
